    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive as long as you can in a harsh world full of monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Periodicity - Hats and scars is a fast paced bullet heaven, auto-shooter, survivers  game set in the wild west. In this DEMO Prepare for the fight in a small village. Venture into the woods to battle against hordes of monsters, bandits and unknown horrors. Beat big boss monster, get loot, buy permanent upgrades and do it again. All while wearing a cool hat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303610/extras/c6ef75b4a935955e5d9b8bb239e4680a.poster.avif?t=1740926618\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303610/extras/c6ef75b4a935955e5d9b8bb239e4680a.webm?t=1740926618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303610/extras/c6ef75b4a935955e5d9b8bb239e4680a.mp4?t=1740926618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get permanent upgrades from merchants</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use different weapons fitting your play style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to get the high score</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless mode and leaderbord </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
